      "bookmarkId": "33117907_4_557-604",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "557-604",
      "markText": "庸碌的人们在地球上为了土地、石油和宗教信仰等琐事争吵不休，而这一切都在我们的认知面前黯然失色。",
      "totalCount": 828,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=557&rangeEnd=604",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=557&rangeEnd=604"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_4_1735-1749",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1735-1749",
      "markText": "进化没有远见，也不计划未来。",
      "totalCount": 666,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1735&rangeEnd=1749",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1735&rangeEnd=1749"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_4_6331-6365",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6331-6365",
      "markText": "能够生在当代是幸福的，因为我们知道如此之多，而且还可以期待知道更多。",
      "totalCount": 340,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6331&rangeEnd=6365",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6331&rangeEnd=6365"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_5_1014-1039",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1014-1039",
      "markText": "曾经最强烈的一次撞击甚至把地球撞出一块形成了月球。",
      "totalCount": 340,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1014&rangeEnd=1039",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1014&rangeEnd=1039"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_6_3014-3052",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3014-3052",
      "markText": "正如遗传学家詹姆斯·克罗所说：老男人的精子是威胁整个族群健康的最大突变灾难。",
      "totalCount": 336,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3014&rangeEnd=3052",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3014&rangeEnd=3052"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_7_3554-3577",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3554-3577",
      "markText": "我们所有的能量都来自食物中释放出来的一缕阳光。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3554&rangeEnd=3577",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3554&rangeEnd=3577"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_13_13462-13536",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "13462-13536",
      "markText": "基因只是大致决定了大脑里面神经回路的雏形，经验才会明确每一条线路的走向，以及它们代表的意义。绝大多数神经回路的意义都由经验决定，并且直接写在大脑里。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=13462&rangeEnd=13536",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=13462&rangeEnd=13536"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_9_6218-6277",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "6218-6277",
      "markText": "这些罕见的物种比如蛭形轮虫，算是生物学家眼中的佼佼者，坚贞而特立于这个沉溺于性的浊世中，一路走来宛如穿过红灯区的和尚。",
      "totalCount": 260,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6218&rangeEnd=6277",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=6218&rangeEnd=6277"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_11_25862-25952",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "25862-25952",
      "markText": "比较有趣的是，昆虫可以看到紫外线，因此很多在我们看来是白色的花，在昆虫眼里其实充满了不同颜色与模式。这也就是为何世上有这么多白色的花朵，因为对于传粉者来说，它们其实充满了各种条纹。",
      "totalCount": 224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=25862&rangeEnd=25952",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=25862&rangeEnd=25952"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_14_14843-14891",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "14843-14891",
      "markText": "只有我们大部分时间都处于饥饿状态，才可能通过阻断胰岛素信号来延长寿命，而且潜在的代价是没有子嗣。",
      "totalCount": 221,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=14843&rangeEnd=14891",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=14843&rangeEnd=14891"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_9_20164-20223",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "20164-20223",
      "markText": "性最大的好处就在于它让好的基因有机会通过重组，脱离那些共存在遗传背景中的垃圾，同时保存了族群里大量被隐藏的遗传多样性。",
      "totalCount": 220,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=20164&rangeEnd=20223",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=20164&rangeEnd=20223"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_13_19281-19363",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "19281-19363",
      "markText": "我们对于自然物质的特性了解得还不够深入，所以不知道神经元如何把无生命的物质转换成主观感觉。如果电子可以既是波又是粒子，那为何灵魂和物质不会是同一件事情的一体两面呢？",
      "totalCount": 216,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=19281&rangeEnd=19363",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=19281&rangeEnd=19363"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_4_5236-5294",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5236-5294",
      "markText": "尽管组成这两种蛋白质的每块积木都随着时间变迁被替换掉了，但是它们拼出的整体结构(同时结构决定功能)却被进化保存下来。",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5236&rangeEnd=5294",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5236&rangeEnd=5294"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_11_16914-16994",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "16914-16994",
      "markText": "一旦幼虫找到合适的场所，就会紧紧粘上去，接下来既然已经用不上脑子，脑子就会慢慢被吸收掉(英国进化学家史蒂夫·琼斯曾打趣说道，这项特技必定会让许多大学教授钦佩)。",
      "totalCount": 209,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=16914&rangeEnd=16994",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=16914&rangeEnd=16994"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_5_1115-1144",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1115-1144",
      "markText": "这是一个永不平衡、无止境躁动的世界，是一个发烧的婴儿星球。",
      "totalCount": 176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1115&rangeEnd=1144",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1115&rangeEnd=1144"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_5_1614-1663",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1614-1663",
      "markText": "人择原理认为，如果宇宙中出现生命的概率是千万亿分之一，那在这千万亿行星中出现生命的概率就接近于1。",
      "totalCount": 176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1614&rangeEnd=1663",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1614&rangeEnd=1663"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_13_24396-24456",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "24396-24456",
      "markText": "意识追根究底只关乎生与死，无关于人类那登峰造极的心智。如果我们真的想要了解意识从何而来，首先要把自己从框架中移出去才行。",
      "totalCount": 176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=33117907&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=24396&rangeEnd=24456",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/26d32ff071f956d326d36a5?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=24396&rangeEnd=24456"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "33117907_5_607-684",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "607-684",
      "markText": "彼时日夜不断地交替，地球上的白昼最多不过五六个小时。地球绕着地轴发疯似的旋转。而月亮距离地球也比现在近得多，所以看起来异常巨大、沉重且具威胁性地挂在天上。",
